WF-003 | Open delinquency bucket from Buckets table | actor: Admin (authenticated user with configuration privileges) | branch: none | terminal: Open Bucket | on_success: opens delinquency bucket details
WF-004 | Create Delinquency Bucket (with one or more Bucket Ranges) | actor: Admin (authenticated user with configuration privileges) | branch: none | terminal: Create | on_success: creates delinquency bucket
</workflows>

